{"tid":1655281,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米手機強制安裝「上報App」","createTime":"2019-10-15T03:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T13:45:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df99e5036f543ee9ee981092bff3c9704663de3f","tid":1655281,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191014/FKITJNZTX6SYYZQZSUFZMRWNPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191014%2FFKITJNZTX6SYYZQZSUFZMRWNPI%2F&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9Ex5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=f1c043c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191014%2FFKITJNZTX6SYYZQZSUFZMRWNPI%2F&h=cc04606f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191014/FKITJNZTX6SYYZQZSUFZMRWNPI/</a><br />\n<br />\n小米手機強制安裝「上報App」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191015/large/1571070154_6c30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191015%2Flarge%2F1571070154_6c30.jpg&h=f8a49d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小米指「MIUI BI數據上報」為預設的應用程式，主要採集小米手機的手機激活、活躍數據等。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有小米（1810）手機用戶於網上討論區投訴，指手機自動更新後，強制安裝「MIUI BI數據上報」App，害怕個人資料會自動上載。<br />\n<br />\n官方：數據存放新加坡<br />\n<br />\n記者曾到小米商城搜尋「數據上報」，並未找到相關應用程式，疑只供手機更新時自動安裝。公司中期報告中顯示，「我們多維度的數據讓我們能夠不斷提升演算法能力和提升用戶體驗。信息流及搜索等服務有助於豐富我們的廣告客戶群。」現時小米大數據網頁顯示，覆蓋用戶達2.6億，設備達2,400萬，「數據上報」可能與擴大用戶量有關。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》就事件向小米查詢，公司回應指，「MIUI BI數據上報」為預設在小米手機系統的應用程式，主要採集小米手機的手機激活、活躍數據等。香港用戶的相關數據是存放位於新加坡的伺服器，作公司內部完善用戶體驗及計算售後服務期限等用途，而小米收集數據亦嚴格遵守所在地區適用的法律法規要求。<br />\n<br />\n記者翻查小米於9月更新的《隱私政策》，指明「根據法律法規規定要求，小米可能有必要披露您的個人資訊。就國家安全、執法或具有公眾重要性的其他事情而言，披露是必須的或適當的。」"},{"pid":"ffd0e299056b9badf526569178762e8a924f2303","tid":1655281,"uid":312242,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T03:51:08.000Z","msg":"用支那機去插ROM係常識"},{"pid":"8d9258b9676a42a475525b6a239ec560a6ae0dcc","tid":1655281,"uid":5399,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用屌米既人全部送中"},{"pid":"820e55aa780118732e796c511fb454739163acbb","tid":1655281,"uid":164985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"係邊個提問"},{"pid":"d5c5b339c52f4bbadae4da2edc7850e122a9f9b5","tid":1655281,"uid":48080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:25:49.000Z","msg":"佢係咪覺得話擺新加坡d人就會覺得好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea747b02547bc65c045cfce73e3a2539984a19e","tid":1655281,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"賤民係無私穩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1143309b575f2981d5658642843c3c688ca228","tid":1655281,"uid":1377,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"用小米走去擔心個人私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44914bf9b7be123b9e666be5188d7131c69cc47","tid":1655281,"uid":13303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d5c5b339c52f4bbadae4da2edc7850e122a9f9b5","tid":1655281,"uid":48080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:25:49.000Z","msg":"佢係咪覺得話擺新加坡d人就會覺得好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:11:41.000Z","msg":"坡共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89cbfdf0f6ed625e5797d54239de93b81a0ad774","tid":1655281,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr